  <body>
    <button class="w3-center w3-button cm-button" onclick="location.href='/ar';" style="width:100%;">This experience uses Augmented Reality (AR) technologies. If this is your first time experiencing such things then you might like to click here.</button>

    <div class="w3-display-container cm-imagepane" style="width:100%;">
      <img src="/static/backgrounds/main.png" alt="" style="width: 100%;">

      <div class="w3-display-middle">
        <div class="cm-h1 w3-xlarge w3-center" style="transform: translateY(-1000%);">
          Click on one of the elements of the scene to learn more!
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w3-display-middle w3-row" style="width:100%;height:100%;">
        <div class="w3-col s4 w3-center" style="transform: translate(-10%, 60%);">
          <!-- LEFT -->
          <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity" style="height:15%; width:75%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/left/poster';"></button>
          <div class="w3-row">
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-cell" style="height:30%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/left/far';"></button>
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-cell" style="height:30%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/left/near';"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w3-col s4 w3-center">
          <!-- CENTER -->
          <div class="w3-row" style="transform: translate(5%, 45%);">
            <button class="w3-button w3-col s4 w3-center w3-opacity" style="height:50%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/left/legs';"></button>
            <button class="w3-button w3-col s4 w3-center w3-opacity" style="height:50%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/printer';"></button>
            <button class="w3-button w3-col s4 w3-center w3-opacity" style="height:50%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/right/legs';"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w3-col s4 w3-center" style="transform: translate(10%, 60%);">
          <!-- RIGHT -->
          <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity" style="height:15%; width:75%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/right/poster';"></button>
          <div class="w3-row">
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-cell" style="height:30%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/right/near';"></button>
            <button class="w3-container w3-button w3-opacity w3-cell" style="height:30%; width:30%;" onclick="location.href='/t/main/right/far';"></button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- LAST -->
      <div class="w3-display-bottommiddle cm-scroll-indicator w3-round-large w3-xxxlarge" style="transform: translate(-50%, -350%)">
        VV SCROLL TO READ MORE VV
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- infopane -->
    <div class="w3-container cm-infopane">
      <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
      <div class="cm-h1 w3-xxxlarge w3-center">
        Additive Manufacting Kiosk
      </div>
      <div class="cm-h1 w3-large">
        The goal of this kiosk was to create an experience where the user can learn about the everyday benefits of additive manufacturing and how this futuristic technology is something that everyone can utilize.
      </div>
